metadata.name: Nymph
metadata.description:
"Nymph" is a captivating artwork that embodies the grace and allure of a mythical being. With intricate details and subtle colors, it invites viewers into a world of enchantment and fascination.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
